Package: aoh
Type: Package
Version: 0.0.0.99999
Title: Area of Habitat Maps
Description: Generate Area of Habitat maps for species distributions.
    Maps are produced following procedures outlined by Brooks et al. (2019)
    (<doi:10.1016/j.tree.2019.06.009>). They are derived using species'
    distribution data from the International Union for Conservation
    of Nature (IUCN) Red List of Threatened Species
    (<https://www.iucnredlist.org/>),
    terrestrial habitat classification data from Jung et al. (2020)
    (<doi:10.1038/s41597-020-00599-8>), and elevation data from Amatulli et al.
    (2018) (<doi:10.1038/sdata.2018.40>).
